{"tid":2517354,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"假內地官員指洗黑錢 擎天半島七旬富婆被騙2000萬元","createTime":"2021-05-05T09:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T09:43:24.000Z","uid":89939,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8d58ac2fafe6db96e2cf8fc97d277d6897053fa2","tid":2517354,"uid":89939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6gU1szO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6gU1szO.png&h=cdc57193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方4月16日接獲一名70歲本地女子報案，指她較早前接獲一名陌生男子來電，對方自稱內地執法人員並指報案人涉及一宗刑事案件，要求報案人交出銀行戶口資料以協助調查。報案人按指示交出有關資料，其後發現戶口內約2千萬港元被轉帳到多個本地戶口，懷疑被騙，遂報案。<br />\n<br />\n  油尖警區刑事調查隊第七隊人員接手調查，案件列作以欺騙手段取得財產，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n  消息指，受騙老婦居住於擎天半島，於今年3月18日接獲騙徒來電，對方自稱為內地官員，並指事主涉嫌洗黑錢，要求她提供銀行戶口資料及密碼。老婦遵指示提供7個銀行戶口資料，對方聲稱戶口內款項會被暫時轉走，以作調查之用，要求她保密，亦不要檢查其戶口。<br />\n<br />\n  老婦其後起疑心，檢查後發現其2000萬款項，分別由4個戶口經網上理財服務轉走，於是報警。老婦聲稱並沒有為意過坊間電騙手法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算當所分20次, 每次一百萬, 要比咩資料先唔會驚動銀行通知戶口持有人<br />\n<br />\n香港大把有錢廢老, 錢真易呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ad1ed30d3222b44eddb85b95f74c29a2200a2c","tid":2517354,"uid":51294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:20:07.000Z","msg":"身有屎"},{"pid":"af3133bd95cf2c4ffcc0bae7201b52f8eced9f59","tid":2517354,"uid":59511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:21:22.000Z","msg":"我都想有兩千萬閒錢俾人呃下<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621693a019e91482ecdc2b190991667e6b2015f5","tid":2517354,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:22:16.000Z","msg":"呢D係咪撐起樓市既北水？<br />\n<br />\n又真係幾疊水"},{"pid":"c590a2bfa73f760db4651393a8082c2d525d3748","tid":2517354,"uid":46947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:22:28.000Z","msg":"洗黑錢過數話你知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad56055a94f99a76cfb8817f9c33fe30b783ec35","tid":2517354,"uid":224533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:22:29.000Z","msg":"隔籬嗰篇在香港致富的方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d58a443aa09c1a9e45c8e0637601aef1df1b8a3","tid":2517354,"uid":187876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:23:43.000Z","msg":"香港做老千最正, 呃到一次已經退得休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你打工幾耐先儲到2千萬?"},{"pid":"a5e97c3cb72e3726602a9a7356deed2009608e97","tid":2517354,"uid":198841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:24:37.000Z","msg":"原來係rosemary阿媽，呃極都仲有"},{"pid":"f5a8245e50f5546cac187ffe800beb2a67f647ad","tid":2517354,"uid":397286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:26:22.000Z","msg":"有2000萬都咁撚豬兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa3de7f5f0610996b9fb26447a329d0c9f889fa","tid":2517354,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:26:25.000Z","msg":"個個禮拜都有呢啲騙案<br />\n不過無幾多個拉到"},{"pid":"0dad6c33420d576f79dc21d9a6d0cbc0c6204ead","tid":2517354,"uid":253954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad56055a94f99a76cfb8817f9c33fe30b783ec35","tid":2517354,"uid":224533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:22:29.000Z","msg":"隔籬嗰篇在香港致富的方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"我第一時間都係諗到呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6a23b7d9e3685250e70342fe55a45bd3344b71","tid":2517354,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:31:05.000Z","msg":"國安大法好"},{"pid":"2ee5deb1c179ada7450cd6c26b083d661fb1d486","tid":2517354,"uid":23120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:32:24.0